item.title: Login with Amazon Cognito
item.description: Create an AWS Account In this section, you sign up for an AWS account. If you already have an AWS account, skip this step. When you sign up for Amazon Web Services (AWS), your AWS account is automatically signed up for all AWS services, including SageMaker. You are charged only for the services that you use. To create an AWS account Open https://portal.aws.amazon.com/billing/signup. Follow the online instructions.
